17-05-17T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用開CREAM MASK<br />\n<br />\nPAPER既用親塊臉都痕痕地咁</blockquote><br />\nPaper我怕會好快乾 cream又好懶 多數用凝膠面膜 Hydra Gel Mask"},{"pid":"2bf1ccbfadf07bd56f861751c3c1e3af8c1a53c6","tid":246494,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問<br />\n咁個paraben有咩唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢問題唔大 但盡量都少啲接觸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24996dfe2c1be08e87d0735c0020f5839aa35054","tid":246494,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實仲想講吓潤唇膏 因為潤唇膏都有啲有害成份要留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6454244cb3e0bc8b726ceb8e76695f575e158a8b","tid":246494,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實仲想講吓潤唇膏 因為潤唇膏都有啲有害成份要留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢有其他成份係補到 呢個我就無留意"},{"pid":"dd0b26e5e4fb8e2d53314c19ba70d3ad2559b26a","tid":246494,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:04:57.000Z","msg":"試咗「春雨」同「JAYJUN」<br />\n其實都有防腐劑（不過都正常 人哋做生意）<br />\n春雨夠貼面 多汁 面膜紙又薄 用完塊面唔會黏黏 <br />\nJayjun brightening隻面膜紙比較厚 唔同一般面膜紙 但貼面 同都夠汁 啲精華易吸收 一樣唔會黏 吸收得好過春雨 <br />\n幾啱一日一pack嘅選擇<br />\n春雨就試咗幾日 無敏感<br />\nJayjun一開始上面會有啲吉吉哋 應該係因為brightening嘅精華比較刺激 如果易敏感嘅人可能要留意 不過我接受到 敷完之後都無啲吉吉哋嘅刺痛感"},{"pid":"163037b0848e9b8af03d45e1cdd7f79f163ee3a4","tid":246494,"uid":73848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"用開fancl dhc 學野"},{"pid":"b6d74b751fb4c55c8178a